      <title>好莱坞明星银行因风险控制失败被罚款 6500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-31/rbc-s-city-national-is-fined-65-million-by-occ-for-risk-control-failures</link>
